font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:ES">Sub Bagian Keuangan mempunyai tugas menyusun rencana anggaran dan mengelola administrasi keuangan serta menyusun laporan pertanggungjawaban pengelolaan anggaran. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom: 9.0pt;margin-left:26.95pt;text-indent:-26.95pt;mso-list:l43 level1 lfo35; tab-stops:list 27.0pt"><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family: Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:PT-BR"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">(2)<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">         </span></span></span><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:PT-BR">Uraian tugas sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) adalah<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">  </span>sebagai berikut : <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom: 6.0pt;margin-left:53.9pt;text-indent:-26.95pt;mso-list:l43 level2 lfo35; tab-stops:list .75in left 58.5pt"><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:PT-BR"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">a.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">            </span></span></span><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:PT-BR">menyiapkan bahan dan menyusun petunjuk teknis penyusunan anggaran dan pengelolaan penataausahaan<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">  </span>keuangan ;<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom: 6.0pt;margin-left:53.9pt;text-indent:-26.95pt;mso-list:l43 level2 lfo35; tab-stops:list .75in left 58.5pt"><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:PT-BR"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">b.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">            </span></span></span><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:PT-BR">menyiapkan bahan penyusunan rencana anggaran belanja tidak