ngevaluasi kegiatan peringatan dini terjadinya bencana ;<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">  </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom: 6.0pt;margin-left:.75in;text-indent:-27.0pt;mso-list:l15 level1 lfo20; tab-stops:list .75in left 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><span lang="ES" style="font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language: ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">g.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">            </span></span></span><span lang="ES" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:ES">menyusun program, mengoordinasikan, membina, mengendalikan dan mengevaluasi kegiatan mitigasi bencana ; dan<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:6.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom: 6.0pt;margin-left:.75in;text-indent:-27.0pt;mso-list:l15 level1 lfo20; tab-stops:list .75in left 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><span lang="ES" style="font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language: ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">h.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">            </span></span></span><span lang="ES" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:ES">melaksanakan tugas-tugas lain yang diberikan oleh Kepala Pelaksana sesuai bidang tugas dan tanggung jawabnya.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom: 9.0pt;margin-left:.5in;text-indent:-.5in;mso-list:l43 level1 lfo35;tab-stops: list 27.0pt left 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><span lang="ES" style="font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:ES"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">(3)<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">         </span></span></span><span lang="ES" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:ES">Unsur-unsur organisasi Bidang Pencegahan dan Kesiagaan adalah<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">  </span>:<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:9.0pt;margin-right:0in;margi