 analisis risiko bencana, penegakan tata ruang dan penerapan persyaratan standar teknis penanggulangan bencana.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="margin-top:12.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom: 6.0pt;margin-left:26.95pt;text-indent:-26.95pt"><span lang="ES" style="font-family: Arial;mso-ansi-language:ES">(2)<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">    </span>Uraian tugas sebagaimana dimaksud pada ayat (1) adalah :<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyTextIndent" style="margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom: 5.0pt;margin-left:53.9pt;text-align:justify;text-indent:-26.95pt;mso-list:l44 level1 lfo38; tab-stops:list .75in left 1.25in 1.5in 1.75in"><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language: PT-BR"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">a.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">            </span></span></span><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:PT-BR">menyiapkan bahan dan menyusun rencana kegiatan pencegahan bencana ;<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyTextIndent" style="margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom: 5.0pt;margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-27.0pt;mso-list:l44 level1 lfo38; tab-stops:list .75in left 1.25in 1.5in 1.75in"><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language: PT-BR"><span style="mso-list:Ignore">b.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">            </span></span></span><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:PT-BR">menyiapkan bahan koordinasi, pembinaan dan pengendalian pencegahan bencana ;<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyTextIndent" style="margin-top:5.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom: 5.0pt;margin-left:.75in;text-align:justify;text-indent:-27.0pt;mso-list:l44 level1 lfo38; tab-stops:list .75in left 1.25in 1.5in 1.75in"><span lang="PT-BR" style="font-family:Arial;mso-fareast-font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language: PT-BR"><span style="