 style="mso-spacerun:yes">              </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="tab-stops:.75in 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="SV" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:SV">SEKRETARIS DAERAH PROVINSI KALIMANTAN SELATAN,<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="tab-stops:.75in 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="SV" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:SV"><o:p> </o:p></span></b></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="tab-stops:.75in 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="SV" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:SV"><o:p> </o:p></span></b></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="tab-stops:.75in 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="SV" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:SV"><o:p> </o:p></span></b></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="tab-stops:.75in 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="SV" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:SV"><o:p> </o:p></span></b></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="tab-stops:.75in 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="SV" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:SV"><o:p> </o:p></span></b></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="tab-stops:.75in 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="SV" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:SV"><span style="mso-spacerun:yes">                          </span>H.M.<span style="mso-spacerun:yes">   </span>MUCHLIS GAFURI<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="line-height:50%;tab-stops:.75in 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><b style="mso-bidi-font-weight:normal"><span lang="SV" style="font-family:Arial; mso-ansi-language:SV"><o:p> </o:p></span></b></p>  <p class="MsoBodyText" style="tab-stops:.75in 81.0pt 99.0pt 117.0pt"><span lang="SV" style="font-family:Arial;mso-ansi-language:SV">BERITA